Changelog for PopLib version 1.4:

General
=======
* Added the V14 demo, showcases: new blend modes (usage of SDL3), TTF text.
* Added x64 support.
* Removed WideString
* Added macOS (partial) + Linux support.
* Added optional Discord RPC support
* Added Chipmunk physics
* Added Dear ImGui support for debug UI's
* Replaced the normal .pak archives with .gpak (NEW!!!!!!!!!)

Scripting
=========
* Added Lua scripting support

AppBase
===========
* Replaced the Windows API input parsing with SDL3 events.
* The demo projects now use PopApp instead of AppBase (you can still use AppBase, but it's gonna miss out on new additions PopApp has)

Graphics
================================
* Replaced the DirectX/DirectDraw rendering system with SDL3.

Audio
================================
* Replaced DSound with OpenAL.

BASS related:
=============
* Replaced BASS with libopenmpt

ImageLib
=============
* removed JPEG2000 support.